Dear Klaow,


You now that R is case-sensitive? That is, see the following:


# Set

interven <- "pzq"

# Then

interven=="pzq" # provides
[1] TRUE

# However,

interven=="PZQ" # provides
[1] FALSE


That is, you have to spell the values in the code exactly as spelled in 
the data set.


Best,

Gerta



